{"tid":2093653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察檢取被捕人士DNA，話有助調查","createTime":"2020-07-04T04:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:04:04.000Z","uid":78047,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b015d006d64eb95d221f90a95c1993b13d2d976f","tid":2093653,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:02:21.000Z","msg":"警方回覆本台查詢時表示，共向10名涉嫌違反《港區國安法》的被捕人士，檢取其DNA樣本，保安局局長李家超出席一個電台節目後，被問到檢取DNA的原因時回應指，警方是根據《警隊條例》，調查刑事案件時，如認為抽取樣本有助調查，並可證明一些罪行，則可行使權力，按情況及案件內容抽取樣本。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港區國安法 #保安局局長 #李家超 #警隊條例 #DNA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4F0LQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4F0LQg.jpg&h=79c0ba49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfc66e6ba9c6f3b3055654fce4d5353522d740b1","tid":2093653,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"檢測港獨基因"},{"pid":"4c342d69b9803905147554f0e6b5baffb65cfcd2","tid":2093653,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}